Submodules

Efficient way to load or handle all submodules for a specific package.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Submodules

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Submodules

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Submodules

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Submodules

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Submodules/


